Louis Joe LE FORCE, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 13662. United States Court of Appeals Fifth Circuit. June 2, 1952. Rehearing Denied July 2, 1952. Clyde G. Hood, Howard Dailey, Dallas, Tex., for appellant. Lester L. May, Asst. U. S. Atty., Frank B. Potter, U. S. Atty., Dallas, Tex., for appellee.

Before HOLMES, STRUM, and RIVES, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment appealed from is affirmed.
